      "instruction": "<p>Once the ciabatta is slightly cooled, rub the sliced-side of the <strong>chopped</strong> <strong>garlic </strong>over it (not a fan of raw garlic? Only use a little!)</p><p>Spoon on the <strong>tomate topping </strong>– this is your <strong>pan con tomate</strong></p>",
